Package: mstratal
Title: Multivariate optimal stratification and allocation for stratified sampling scheme 
Version: 1.01
Authors@R: person("Robert", "Wieczorkowski", email = "R.Wieczorkowski@stat.gov.pl", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Package can be used for computation of multivariate optimal stratification and allocation in stratified sampling.
   New numerical method is implemented for determination of the strata boundaries given the number of strata and target precision of estimation.  
Depends: R (>= 3.5.1)
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: 
    matrixStats,
    nloptr,
    stratallo
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
URL: https://github.com/rwieczor/mstratal
BugReports: https://github.com/rwieczor/mstratal/issues
